Package: com.android.builder.profile

[Java] Enum ExecutionType

      • com.android.builder.profile.ExecutionType

      • Defines a type of processing. Use range for similar categories events : 0-1000 initial setup 1000-2000 application related task creation 2000-3000 library related task creation 3000-4000 Tasks related events.
